            <head xml:id="bHY6yh-d35529-Hd1e108">Rubrica 1</head>
           <head xml:id="bHY6yh-d35529-Hd1e111" type="question-title">De petitionibus et rogationibus beneficiorum: et exauditionibus vel de negationibus</head>
    
    <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d35529-d1e114">
               <lb ed="#V" n="69"/>Uintus liber secunde partis
      <lb ed="#V" n="70"/>tractat de beneficiis: sub his ti
      <lb ed="#V" n="71"/>tulis sequentibus. 
    </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d35529-d1e123">
               <lb ed="#V" n="72"/>
      ¶ De petitionibus et rogatio
      <lb ed="#V" n="73" break="no"/>nibus beneficiorum: et exauditio
      <lb ed="#V" n="74" break="no"/>nibus vel de negationibus.
      <lb ed="#V" n="75"/>Rubrica prima.
    </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d35529-d1e134">
               <lb ed="#V" n="76"/><ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d35529-Rd1e130">ISocrates in exhorta
      <lb ed="#V" n="77" break="no"/>tionibus. c
      <lb ed="#V" n="78"/>2.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d35529-Qd1e142">Siquidem elegantius vteris ami
        <lb ed="#V" n="79" break="no"/>cis si minime praestoleris eorum praeces: et
        <lb ed="#V" n="80"/>vltro sibi cum exigit tempus auxilieris.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d35529-d1e151">
               <lb ed="#V" n="81"/>
             ¶ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d35529-Rd1e150">Aristoteles rethoricorum lib. 2. c. 6.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d35529-Qd1e155">Factiua
        <lb ed="#V" n="82"/>amicitie est gratia et non requisitum facere.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d35529-d1e161">
               <lb ed="#V" n="83"/>
             ¶ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d35529-Rd1e162">Salustiuis in catilinario:</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d35529-Qd1e165">Auxilium ab omni
        <lb ed="#V" n="84"/>bus petas: etiam ab insimis.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d35529-d1e171">
               <lb ed="#V" n="85"/>
             ¶ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d35529-Rd1e174">Oratius in sermonibus li. i. smo. 3.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d35529-Qd1e175">Omnibus hoc
        <lb ed="#V" n="86"/>vitium est causatatoribus iter amicos: vt non dispo
        <lb ed="#V" n="87" break="no"/>nant animum causatare rogati: Inuisi numquam desistant.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d35529-d1e183">
               <lb ed="#V" n="88"/>
             ¶ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d35529-Rd1e188">Tullius de amincitia:</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d35529-Qd1e187">Hec lex in amicitia
        <lb ed="#V" n="89"/>sanciatur: vt neque rogemus res turpes: neque
        <lb ed="#V" n="90"/>faciamus rogati. <!--120.xml-->
        <pb ed="#V" n="47-r"/>
                  <cb ed="#V" n="a"/>
               </quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d35529-d1e201">
               <lb ed="#V" n="1"/>
             ¶ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d35529-Rd1e208">Ouidius epistolarum. 7. epi</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d35529-Qd1e205">Perdere ver
        <lb ed="#V" n="2" break="no"/>ba leue est.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d35529-d1e211"> /
               <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d35529-Rd1e218">Idem sine titulo seu amorum
        <lb ed="#V" n="3"/>li. 3. et fi. e. 11</ref>
        <lb ed="#V" n="4"/><quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d35529-Qd1e213">Desine blandicias: et verba potentia quondam
        <lb ed="#V" n="5"/>Perdere non ego sum stultus vt ante fui.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d35529-d1e224">
               <lb ed="#V" n="6"/> /
               <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d35529-Rd1e235">Idem de arte amandi li. i.</ref>
        <lb ed="#V" n="7"/><quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d35529-Qd1e228">Flectitur iratus: voce rogante deus.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d35529-d1e234">
               <lb ed="#V" n="8"/> /
               <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d35529-Rd1e246">Idem methamorpho. libro. 8.</ref>
        <lb ed="#V" n="9"/><quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d35529-Qd1e238">Ignauis praecibus: fortuna repugnat.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d35529-d1e244"> /
            <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d35529-Rd1e255">Li. 9.</ref>
        <lb ed="#V" n="10"/><quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d35529-Qd1e246">Id pete quod fas est.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d35529-d1e252"> /
            <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d35529-Rd1e264">Idem de ponto li. 2. e. 9</ref>
        <lb ed="#V" n="11"/><quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d35529-Qd1e254">Con spicitur nunquam: meliore potentia causa:
        <lb ed="#V" n="12"/>Quam quotiens varias non finit esse preces.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d35529-d1e262">
               <lb ed="#V" n="13"/>
             ¶ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d35529-Rd1e277">Seneca tragediarum in hypolito. c. 6.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d35529-Qd1e266">Qui
        <lb ed="#V" n="14"/>timide rogat: docet negare.</quote><ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d35529-Rd1e283">Idem de benefi
        <lb ed="#V" n="15" break="no"/>ciis li. 3.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d35529-Qd1e274">Si contingit interuenire plura rogam
        <lb ed="#V" n="16"/>tis verba interdicenda sunt: ne rogati videa
        <lb ed="#V" n="17" break="no"/>mur: sed certiores facti statim promittamus:
        <lb ed="#V" n="18"/>facturosque nos antequam interpellemur ipsa fe
        <lb ed="#V" n="19" break="no"/>stinatione approbemus.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d35529-d1e283"> /
            <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d35529-Rd1e302">Idem declam.
        <lb ed="#V" n="20"/>li. 2 c. 7.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d35529-Qd1e285">Nemo fortiter negantem interum roga
        <lb ed="#V" n="21" break="no"/>uit.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d35529-d1e294"> /
            <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d35529-Rd1e316">Idem in prouerb.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d35529-Qd1e296">Minus decipitur cum
        <lb ed="#V" n="22"/>negatur celeriter. Negandi causa: auaro num
        <lb ed="#V" n="23" break="no"/>quam deficit.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d35529-d1e304">
               <lb ed="#V" n="24"/>
             ¶ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d35529-Rd1e330">Ualerius maxi. li. 6. ti.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d35529-Qd1e308">grauiter dicta aut
        <lb ed="#V" n="25"/>facta: Publius rutilius: cum amici cuiusdam
        <lb ed="#V" n="26"/>iniuste rogationi resisteret: atque is per summam.
        <lb ed="#V" n="27"/>indignationem dixisset: quid ergo opus est mi
        <lb ed="#V" n="28" break="no"/>hi amicitia tua si quod rogo non facis. Im
        <lb ed="#V" n="29" break="no"/>mo quid mihi tua: si propter te aliquid inho
        <lb ed="#V" n="30" break="no"/>neste facturus sum.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d35529-d1e325"> /
            <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d35529-Rd1e351">Li. 7. ti.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d35529-Qd1e327">Sapienter di
        <lb ed="#V" n="31" break="no"/>cta aut facta: Socrates humane sapientie: qua
        <lb ed="#V" n="32" break="no"/>si quoddam terrestre oraculum: nihil vltra petem
        <lb ed="#V" n="33" break="no"/>dum a diis immortalibus arbitrabatur quam vt bo
        <lb ed="#V" n="34" break="no"/>na tribuerentur: quia hi demum scirent quid
        <lb ed="#V" n="35"/>vnicuique esset vtile. Ti. aure dicta aut facta. <!--add ref tag?-->
        <lb ed="#V" n="36"/>Alexander cum ad excidium lansacene vrbis sum
        <lb ed="#V" n="37" break="no"/>mo studio fereretur: progressumque extra me
        <lb ed="#V" n="38" break="no"/>nia anasiminem praeceptorem suum vidisset: quia ma
        <lb ed="#V" n="39" break="no"/>nifestum erat futurum: vt praeces suas ire eius op
        <lb ed="#V" n="40" break="no"/>poneret: non facturum se quod petisset iurauit
        <lb ed="#V" n="41"/>Tunc anasimenes: peto inquit: vt lansacum
        <lb ed="#V" n="42"/>diruas. Hec velocitas sagittatis oppidum ve
        <lb ed="#V" n="43" break="no"/>tusta nobilitate inclytum exitio cui destinatum
        <lb ed="#V" n="44"/>erat subtraxit.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d35529-d1e361">
               <lb ed="#V" n="45"/>
             ¶ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d35529-Rd1e393">Prosper sub. 91. epigramate.</ref> <!--120.xml-->
        <cb ed="#V" n="b"/>
        <lb ed="#V" n="46"/><quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d35529-Qd1e365">Cum deus effectum: praecibus non praestat iniquis.
        <lb ed="#V" n="47"/>Multum concedit: quod nocitura negat.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d35529-d1e377">
               <lb ed="#V" n="48"/>
             ¶ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d35529-Rd1e410">Macrobius saturnaliorum li. 2. c. 18 ex au
        <lb ed="#V" n="49" break="no"/>ctoritate publii.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d35529-Qd1e381">Pars beneficii est quod pe
        <lb ed="#V" n="50" break="no"/>titur si cito neges.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d35529-d1e389">
               <lb ed="#V" n="51"/>
             ¶ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d35529-Rd1e425">Cato. c. 2.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d35529-Qd1e393">Quod iustum est petito: vel quod
        <lb ed="#V" n="52"/>videatur honestum. Nam stultum est pete
        <lb ed="#V" n="53" break="no"/>re: quod possit iure negari.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d35529-d1e402">
               <lb ed="#V" n="54"/>
             ¶ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d35529-Rd1e440">Cassiodorus epistolarum li. 2 epistola 30.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d35529-Qd1e406">Cur
        <lb ed="#V" n="55"/>illud tardemus annuere vnde nulla possu
        <lb ed="#V" n="56" break="no"/>mus damna sustinere.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d35529-d1e414"> /
               <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d35529-Rd1e452">Li. 3 e. 43.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d35529-Qd1e416">Suppli
        <lb ed="#V" n="57" break="no"/>cationem praecepit humanitas.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d35529-d1e422"> /
               <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d35529-Rd1e462">Li. 4. e. 5.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d35529-Qd1e424">Do
        <lb ed="#V" n="58" break="no"/>nare videtur qui vendit rogatus.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d35529-d1e430"> /
               <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d35529-Rd1e472">24. e.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d35529-Qd1e432">Uo
        <lb ed="#V" n="59" break="no"/>tis iusta poscentium tribuat effectus.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d35529-d1e438"> /
               <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d35529-Rd1e482">26 e.</ref>
        <lb ed="#V" n="60"/><quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d35529-Qd1e440">Ipsa est perfecta pietas que antequem flectatur prae
        <lb ed="#V" n="61" break="no"/>cibus nouit considerare fatigatos.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d35529-d1e448"> /
               <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d35529-Rd1e493">Idem de
        <lb ed="#V" n="62"/>amicitia. c. 22</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d35529-Qd1e450">Generosus animus nil magis
        <lb ed="#V" n="63"/>erubescit quam petere.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d35529-d1e459">
               <lb ed="#V" n="64"/>
             ¶ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d35529-Rd1e509">Ualdo. 11 fabu.</ref>
        <lb ed="#V" n="65"/><quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d35529-Qd1e463">Blandimenta praecum vertunt in candida tetrum.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d35529-d1e469">
               <lb ed="#V" n="66"/>
             ¶ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d35529-Rd1e520">Gualterius de castellione li. 6.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d35529-Qd1e473">Repulsam
        <lb ed="#V" n="67"/>Ex merito patitur: qui postulat vlterius quam
        <lb ed="#V" n="68"/>Promeruit: spes quam meritum ni praeuenit a spe
        <lb ed="#V" n="69"/>Deuiat: et verum dat ei presumptio nomen.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d35529-d1e483">
               <lb ed="#V" n="70"/>
             ¶ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d35529-Rd1e536">Mattheus vindoci. de histo. tobie. c 31.</ref>
        <lb ed="#V" n="71"/><quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d35529-Qd1e487">Sepe repulsa iuuat: nocet impetrare repulsa
        <lb ed="#V" n="72"/>Liberat arbitrium munera sumpta ligant.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d35529-d1e495">
               <lb ed="#V" n="73"/> /
               <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d35529-Rd1e549">Capitulo. 39.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d35529-Qd1e499">Est rogo vox miseri: vox im
        <lb ed="#V" n="74" break="no"/>portuna pudoris
        <lb ed="#V" n="75"/>Prodiga meroris: plena fauoris egens.
        <lb ed="#V" n="76"/>Largire rogata roganti: Si poteris.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d35529-d1e509">
               <lb ed="#V" n="77"/>
             ¶ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d35529-Rd1e565">Prouerbia metricum extraordinem li. vag.</ref>
        <lb ed="#V" n="78"/><quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d35529-Qd1e513">Est orare ducum: species violenta iubendi.
        <lb ed="#V" n="79"/>Et quasi nudato supplicat ense potens.</quote>
            </p>
         </div>
